N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 3.4 - Journal of proceedings

State Regulations

The commissioner shall cause a journal to be kept of the
proceedings of the Regents and, as the official record thereof, after approval
by the board, from time to time he shall have copies bound in form suitable for
permanent preservation. Notes
